---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1>Iro's Blog</h1>
				<p>Hello.Nice to meet you.Hope everyday is better for you.</p>
				<p>你好！很高兴见到你，希望你每一天都会变得更好。</p>
				<p>こんにちは！ 初めまして、おあいできて嬉しいです。毎日がもっとよくなりますように。</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 100px 20px 40px;
	}
	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 60px;
		color: #c084a0;
	}
	.hero p {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #888;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}
</style>
